{"tid":1632912,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"呢場抗爭 應該點行落去？","createTime":"2019-10-07T01:07:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T01:27:15.000Z","uid":222190,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"79d7b748b71eafcea71987a504de8a5a874e5f8e","tid":1632912,"uid":222190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:07:11.000Z","msg":"惡意分化言論 互相指罵對方有錯<br />\n大量鼓吹破壞藍店中資店 甚至搞解放軍<br />\n導致抗爭者理念分化 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">7婆想令我地成為 真。暴徒？<br />\n影響國際戰線 人權法通過？停區選？民鬥民？<br />\n</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">我地採用任何攬炒方法 <br />\n逼使港共政府答應訴求？<br />\n若不答應 就同歸於盡？<br />\n懲罰任何撐警 撐政府商店/人 逼使他們就範？<br />\n咁我地咁辛苦文宣 打國際戰線黎做咩？ </span><br />\n- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - <br />\n請大家唔好比仇恨支配；<br />\n每當見到班仆街 濫權 濫捕 濫用私刑<br />\n我地係好嬲 直頭想殺晒班人渣<br />\n<br />\n但我地目標 係要贏呢場仗<br />\n制裁警黑政府 施暴者<br />\n當您行動前 請大家唔好忘記初心<br />\n保持應有紀律 良知<br />\n<br />\n同時注意自己既言論態度<br />\n檢討問題後 加以改善<br />\n停止分化 停止互相指罵<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span></span><br />\n- - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - -"},{"pid":"d27745182ea1296d523b30050d1840aced6daeb3","tid":1632912,"uid":222190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:14:12.000Z","msg":"人人都可以幫手文宣<br />\n<br />\nSolomon Yue呢2條tweet都顯示左個問題<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1632043\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1632043</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6e962319ab28cf534eef1a476885d19e2d144eae","tid":1632912,"uid":222190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:16:15.000Z","msg":"大家唔好放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d56b5a431ea9c8f59fbaac981e759f822a8ae7b1","tid":1632912,"uid":222190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:16:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fc0fd34f99b4ffa8d383bf653ed7af60d18ac5e","tid":1632912,"uid":222190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:16:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"779c13cd94abcaed66fc2e19356b6232b16525e0","tid":1632912,"uid":222190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:18:54.000Z","msg":"從今起 沒有分和理非/勇武<br />\n我地都係手足 同路人"},{"pid":"51b7b2ae40bc7ed3d7e737411e7cdf50de3ebe9f","tid":1632912,"uid":222190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:19:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb37287a92d8a2f757327451f937ec715fd42137","tid":1632912,"uid":222190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:21:33.000Z","msg":"我地係識一手硬 一手軟<br />\n大家唔好再分化啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"944da8e903a2f72051412fed9ebdb0430e017ebb","tid":1632912,"uid":222190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:22:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f0f73eb6064cc265b335983ce11adbc3add6326","tid":1632912,"uid":222190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:24:40.000Z","msg":"我地仲要期望<br />\n可以係煲底下相認<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f067bb44917d71eae88f87e80542bf3eaa01d6c2","tid":1632912,"uid":222190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T01:27:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}